|c4
|p1  sAhasr/as tveS/a .rSabh/aH p/ayasvAn v/i/SvA rUp/ANi vakS/aNAsu b/ibhrat /
     bhadr/aM dAtr/e y/ajamAnAya /SIkSan bArhaspaty/a usr/iyas t/antum /AtAn //1//
|p2  ap/AM y/o /agne pratim/A babh/Uva prabh/UH s/arvasmai p.rthiv/Iva dev/I /
     pit/A vats/AnAM p/atir aghny/AnAM sAhasr/e p/oSe /api naH k.rNotu //2//
|p3  p/umAn ant/arvAn tsth/aviraH p/ayasvAn v/asoH k/abandhaM .rSabh/o bibharti /
     t/am /indrAya path/ibhir devay/Anair hut/am agn/ir vahatu jAt/avedAH //3//
|p4  pit/A vats/AnAM p/atir aghny/AnAM /atho pit/A mahat/AM g/argarANAm /
     vats/o jar/Ayu pratidh/uk pIy/USa Am/ikSA gh.rt/aM t/ad v asya r/etaH //4//
|p5  dev/AnAM bhAg/a upanAh/a eS/o 'p/AM r/asa /oSadhInAM gh.rt/asya /
     s/omasya bhakS/am av.rNIta /Sakr/o b.rh/ann /adrir abhavad y/ac ch/arIram //5//
|p6  s/omena pUrN/aM kal/a/SaM bibharSi tv/astA rup/ANAM janit/A pa/SUn/Am /
     /Siv/As te santu prajanv\a ih/a y/A im/A ny \asm/abhyaM svadhite yaccha y/A am/UH //6//
|p7  /AjaM bibharti gh.rt/am asya r/etaH sAhasr/aH p/oSas t/am u yaj~N/am AhuH /
     /indrasya rUp/am .rSabh/o v/asAnaH s/o asm/An devAH /Siv/a a/itu datt/aH //7//
|p8  /indrasya/ujo v/aruNasya bAh/U a/Sv/inor /aMsau mar/utAm iy/aM kak/ut /
     b/rhasp/atiM s/aMbh.rtam et/am Ahur y/e dh/IrAsaH kav/ayo y/e manIS/iNaH //8//
|p9  da/ivIr v/i/SaH p/ayasvAn /A tanoSi tv/Am /indraM tv/AM s/arasvantam AhuH /
     sah/asraM s/a /ekamukhA dadAti y/o brAhmaN/a .rSabh/am Ajuh/oti //9//
|p10  b/rhasp/atiH savit/A te v/ayo dadhau tv/aSTur vAy/oH p/ary Atm/A ta /Abh.rtaH /
     ant/arikSe m/anasA tvA juhomi barh/iS Te dy/AvAp.rthiv/I ubh/e stAm //10//
|p11  y/a /indra iva dev/eSu g/oSv eti viv/Avadat /
     t/asya .rSabh/asy/A.NgAni brahm/A s/aM stautu bhadr/ayA //11//
|p12  pAr/Sv/e AstAm /anumatyA bh/agasyAstAm anUv/rjau /
     aSThIv/antAv abravIn mitr/o m/amaita/u k/evalAv /iti //12//
|p13  bhas/ad AsId Adity/AnAM /Sr/oNI AstAM b/rhasp/ateH /
     p/ucchaM v/Atasya dev/asya t/ena dhUnoty /oSadhIH //13//
|p14  g/udA Asan tsinIvAly/AH sUry/AyAs tv/acam abruvan /
     utthAt/ur abruvan pad/a .rSabh/aM y/ad /akalpayan //14//
|p15  kroD/a AsIj jAmi/SaMs/asya s/omasya kl/a/So dh.rt/aH /
     dev/AH saMg/atya y/at s/arva .rSabh/aM vy/akalpayan //15//
|p16  t/e k/uSThikAH sar/amAyai kurm/ebhyo adadhuH /Saph/An /
     /Ubadhyam asya kIt/ebhyaH /Svavart/ebhyo adhArayan //16//
|p17  /S/r.NgAbhyAM r/akSa .rSaty /avartim hanti c/akSuSA /
     /S.rN/oti bhadr/aM k/arNAbhyAM g/avAM y/aH p/atir aghny/aH //17//
|p18  /Satay/AjaM s/a yajate na/inaM dunvanty agn/ayaH /
     j/invanti v/i/Sve t/aM dev/A y/o brAhmaN/a .rSabh/am Ajuh/oti //18//
|p19  brAhmaN/ebhya .rSabh/aM dattv/A v/arIyaH k.rNute m/anaH /
     p/uSTiM s/o aghny/AnAM sv/e goSTh/e 'va pa/Syate //19//
|p20  g/AvaH santu praj/AH santv /atho astu tanUbal/am /
     t/at s/arvam /anu manyantAM dev/A .rSabhadAy/ine //20//
|p21  ay/aM pipAna /indra /id ray/iM dadhAtu cetan/Im /
     ay/aM dhen/uM sud/ughAM n/ityavatsAM v/a/SaM duhAM vipa/Sc/itaM par/o div/aH //21//
|p22  pi/S/a.NgarUpo nabhas/o vayodh/A aindr/aH /S/uSmo vi/Sv/arUpo na /Agan /
     /Ayur asm/abhyaM d/adhat praj/AM ca rAy/a/S ca p/oSair abh/i naH sacatAm //22//
|p23  /upeh/opaparcanAsm/in goSTh/a /upa p.r~Nca naH /
     /upa .rSabh/asya y/ad r/eta /upendra t/ava vIry\am //23//
|p24  et/aM vo y/uvAnaM pr/ati dadhmo /atra t/ena kr/IDantI/S carata v/a/SA~M /anu /
     m/A no hAsiSTa jan/uSA subhAgA rAy/a/S ca p/oSair abh/i naH sacadhvam //24//
|c5
|p1  /A nayait/am /A rabhasva suk/rtAM lok/am /api gacchatu prajAn/an /
     tIrtv/A t/amAMsi bahudh/A mah/Anty aj/o n/Akam /A kramatAM t.rt/Iyam //1//
|p2  /indrAya bhAg/aM p/ari tvA nayAmy asm/in yaj~N/e y/ajamAnAya sUr/im /
     y/e no dviS/anty /anu t/An rabhasv/AnAgaso y/ajamAnasya vIr/AH //2//
|p3  pr/a pad/o 'va nenigdhi d/u/ScaritaM y/ac cac/Ara /Suddha/iH /Sapha/ir /A kramatAM prajAn/an /
     tIrtv/A t/amAMsi bahudh/A vip/a/Syann aj/o n/Akam /A kramatAM t.rt/Iyam //3//
|p4  /anu cchya /SyAm/ena tv/acam et/AM vi/Sastar yathAparv\a1s/inA m/Abh/i maMsthAH /
     m/Abh/i druhaH paru/S/aH kalpayainaM t.rt/Iye n/Ake /adhi v/i /Srayainam //4//
|p5  .rc/A kumbh/Im /adhy agna/u /SrayAmy /A si~Ncodak/am /ava dhehy enam /
     pary/AdhattAgn/inA /SamitAraH s.rt/o gacchatu suk/rtAM y/atra lok/aH //5//
|p6  /ut kAm/AtaH p/ari ced /ataptas tapt/Ac car/or /adhi n/AkaM t.rt/Iyam /
     agn/er agn/ir /adhi s/aM babhUvitha jy/otiSmantam abh/i lok/aM jayait/am //6//
|p7  aj/o agn/ir aj/am u jy/otir Ahur aj/aM j/IvatA brahm/aNe d/eyam AhuH /
     aj/as t/amAMsy /apa hanti dUr/am asm/iMl lok/e /Sradd/adhAnena datt/aH //7//
|p8  p/a~NcaudanaH pa~Ncadh/A v/i kramatAm AkraMsy/amAnas tr/INi jy/otIMSi /
     IjAn/AnAM suk/rtAM pr/ehi m/adhyaM t.rt/Iye n/Ake /adhi v/i /Srayasva //8//
|p9  /aj/A roha suk/rtAM y/atra lok/aH /Sarabh/o n/a catt/o 'ti durg/Any eSaH /
     p/a~Ncaudano brahm/aNe dIy/amAnaH s/a dAt/AraM t/rptyA tarpayAti //9//
|p10  aj/as trinAk/e tridiv/e trip.rSTh/e n/Akasya p.rSTh/e dadiv/AMsaM dadhAti /
     p/a~Ncaudano brahm/aNe dIy/amAno vi/Sv/arUpA dhen/uH kAmad/ughAsy /ekA //10//
|p11  et/ad vo jy/otiH pitaras t.rt/IyaM p/a~NcaudanaM brahm/aNe 'j/aM dadAti /
     aj/as t/amAMsy /apa hanti dUr/am asm/iMl lok/e /Sradd/adhAnena datt/aH //11//
|p12  IjAn/AnAM suk/rtAM lok/am /Ipsan p/a~NcaudanaM brahm/aNe 'j/aM dadAti /
     s/a vy\Aptim abh/i lok/aM jayait/aM /Siv/o3 'sm/abhyaM pr/atig.rhIto astu //12//
|p13  aj/o hy \a1gner /ajaniSTa /S/okAd v/ipro v/iprasya s/ahaso vipa/Sc/it /
     iST/aM pUrt/am abh/ipUrtaM v/aSaTk.rtaM t/ad dev/A .rtu/S/aH kalpayantu //13//
|p14  amot/aM v/Aso dadyAd dh/iraNyam /api d/akSiNAm /
     t/athA lok/An ts/am Apnoti y/e divy/A y/e ca p/ArthivAH //14//
|p15  et/As tvAj/opa yantu dh/ArAH somy/A dev/Ir gh.rt/ap.rSThA madhu/Sc/utaH /
     stabhAn p.rthiv/Im ut/a dy/AM n/Akasya p.rSTh/e 'dhi sapt/ara/Smau //15//
|p16  aj/o 'sy /aja svarg/o 'si tv/ayA lok/am /a.NgirasaH pr/AjAnan /
     t/aM lok/aM p/uNyaM pr/a j~NeSam //16//
|p17  y/enA sah/asraM v/ahasi y/enAgne sarvavedas/am /
     t/enem/aM yaj~N/aM no vaha sv\ar dev/eSu g/antave //17//
|p18  aj/aH pakv/aH svarg/e lok/e dadhAti p/a~Ncaudano n/ir.rtiM b/AdhamAnaH /
