|p19  y/aM brAhmaN/e nidadh/e y/aM ca vikS/u y/A vipr/uSa odan/AnAm aj/asya /
     s/arvaM t/ad agne suk.rt/asya lok/e jAnIt/An naH saMg/amane pathIn/Am //19//
