     s/a ebhyo j/itim /id duhe bh/UyobhUyaH /Sv/aH/Svas t/ena tv/aM dviSat/o jahi //16//
|p17  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir v/AtAya maN/im A/S/ave /
     t/am im/aM dev/atA maN/iM pr/aty amu~Ncanta /Sambh/uvam /
     s/a Abhyo v/i/Svam /id duhe bh/UyobhUyaH /Sv/aH/Svas t/ena tv/aM dviSat/o jahi //17//
|p18  .rt/avas t/am abadhnatArtav/As t/am abadhnata /
     saMvatsar/as t/aM baddhv/A s/arvaM bhUt/aM v/i rakSati //18//
|p19  antarde/S/A abadhnata prad/i/Sas t/am abadhnata /
     praj/Apatis.rSTo maN/ir dviSat/o m/e 'dharA~M akaH //19//
|p20  /atharvANo abadhnatAtharvaN/A abadhnata /
     ta/ir med/ino /a.Ngiraso d/asyUnAM bibhiduH p/uras t/ena tv/am dviSat/o jahi //20//
|p21  t/aM dhAt/A pr/aty amu~Ncata s/a bhUt/aM vy \akalpayat /
     t/ena tv/aM dviSat/o jahi //21//
|p22  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamad r/asena sah/a v/arcasA //22//
|p23  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamat sah/a g/obhir ajAv/ibhir /annena praj/ayA sah/a //23//
|p24  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamat sah/a vrIhiyav/AbhyAM m/ahasA bh/UtyA sah/a //24//
|p25  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agaman m/adhor gh.rt/asya dh/ArayA kIl/Alena maN/iH sah/a //25//
|p26  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamad Urj/ayA p/ayasA sah/a dr/aviNena /Sriy/A sah/a //26//
|p27  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamat t/ejasA tv/iSyA sah/a y/a/SasA kIrty\A sah/a //27//
|p28  y/am /abadhnAd b/rhasp/atir dev/ebhyo /asurakSitim /
     s/a mAy/aM maN/ir /Agamat s/arvAbhir bh/UtibhiH sah/a //28//
|p29  t/am im/aM dev/atA maN/iM m/ahyaM dadatu p/uSTaye /
     abhibh/uM kSatrav/ardhanaM sapatnad/ambhanaM maN/im //29//
|p30  br/ahmaNA t/ejasA sah/a pr/ati mu~NcAmi me /Siv/am /
     asapatn/aH sapatnah/A sap/atnAn m/e 'dharA~M akaH //30//
|p31  /uttaraM dviSat/o m/Am ay/aM maN/iH k.rNotu devaj/AH /
     y/asya lok/A im/e tr/ayaH p/ayo dugdh/am up/Asate /
     s/a mAy/am /adhi rohatu maN/iH /Sra/iSThyAya mUrdhat/aH //31//
|p32  y/aM dev/AH pit/aro manuSy\A upaj/Ivanti sarvad/A /
     s/a mAy/am /adhi rohatu maN/iH /Sra/iSThyAya mUrdhat/aH //32//
|p33  y/athA b/Ijam urv/arAyAM k.rST/e ph/Alena r/ohati /
     ev/A m/ayi praj/A pa/S/av/o 'nnamannaM v/i rohatu //33//
|p34  y/asmai tvA yaj~Navardhana m/aNe praty/amucaM /Siv/am /
     t/aM tv/aM /SatadakSiNa m/aNe /SraiSThyAya jinvatAt //34//
|p35  et/am idhm/aM sam/AhitaM juSaN/o /agne pr/ati harya h/omaiH /
     t/asmin vidhema sumat/iM svast/i praj/Am c/akSuH pa/S/Un ts/amiddhe jAt/avedasi br/ahmaNA //35//
|c7
|p1  k/asminn /a.Nge t/apo asy/Adhi tiSThati k/asminn /a.Nga .rt/am asy/Adhy /Ahitam /
