     sugArhapaty/o vit/apann /arAtim uS/AmuSAM /Sr/eyasIM dhehy asma/i //45//
|p46  s/arvAn agne s/ahamAnaH sap/atnAn a/iSAm /UrjaM ray/im asm/Asu dhehi //46//
|p47  im/am /indraM v/ahniM p/aprim anv/ArabhadhvaM s/a vo n/ir vakSad durit/Ad avady/At /
     t/en/Apa hata /S/arum Ap/atantaM t/ena rudr/asya p/ari pAtAst/Am //47//
