|p49  ahorAtr/e /anv eSi b/ibhrat kSemy/as t/iSThan prat/araNaH suv/IraH /
     /anAturAn tsum/anasas talpa b/ibhraj jy/og ev/a naH p/uruSagandhir edhi //49//
