|c4
|p1  d/adAm/Ity ev/a brUyAd /anu cainAm /abhutsata /
     va/S/AM brahm/abhyo y/Acadbhyas t/at praj/Avad /apatyavat //1//
|p2  praj/ayA s/a v/i krINIte pa/S/ubhi/S c/opa dasyati /
     y/a ArSey/ebhyo y/Acadbhyo dev/AnAM g/AM n/a d/itsati //2//
|p3  kUT/ayAsya s/aM /SIryante /SloN/ayA kAt/am ardati /
     baND/ayA dahyante g.rh/AH kAN/ayA dIyate sv/am //3//
|p4  vilohit/o adhiSTh/AnAc chakn/o vindati g/opatim /
     t/athA va/S/AyAH s/aMvidyaM duradabhn/A hy \ucy/ase //4//
