     anAman/At s/aM /SIryante y/A m/ukhenopaj/ighrati //5//
|p6  y/o asyAH k/arNAv Askun/oty /A s/a dev/eSu v.r/Scate /
     l/akSma kurva /iti m/anyate k/anIyaH k.rNute sv/am //6//
|p7  y/ad asyAH k/asmai cid bh/ogAya b/AlAn k/a/S cit prak.rnt/ati /
     t/ataH ki/Sor/A mriyante vats/AM/S ca gh/Atuko v/rkaH //7//
|p8  y/ad asyA g/opatau saty/A l/oma dhv/A.NkSo /ajIhiDat /
     t/ataH kumAr/A mriyante y/akSmo vindaty anAman/At //8//
