     t/at/o 'parUpaM jAyate t/asmAd /avyeSyad /enasaH //9//
|p10  j/AyamAnAbh/i jAyate dev/An ts/abrAhmaNAn va/S/A /
     t/asmAd brahm/abhyo d/eyaiS/A t/ad AhuH sv/asya g/opanam //10//
|p11  y/a enAM van/im Ay/anti t/eSAM dev/ak.rtA va/S/A /
     brahmajy/eyaM t/ad abruvan y/a enAM nipriyAy/ate //11//
|p12  y/a ArSey/ebhyo y/Acadbhyo dev/AnAM g/AM n/a d/itsati /
     /A s/a dev/eSu v.r/Scate brAhmaN/AnAM ca many/ave //12//
|p13  y/o asya sy/Ad va/SAbhog/o any/Am iccheta t/arhi s/aH /
     h/iMste /adattA p/uruSaM yAcit/AM ca n/a d/itsati //13//
|p14  y/athA /Sevadh/ir n/ihito brAhmaN/AnAM t/athA va/S/A /
     t/Am et/ad acch/Ayanti y/asmin k/asmiM/S ca j/Ayate //14//
|p15  sv/am et/ad acchAyanti y/ad va/S/AM brAhmaN/A abh/i /
     y/athainAn any/asmin jinIy/Ad ev/AsyA nir/odhanam //15//
|p16  c/ared ev/A traihAyaN/Ad /avij~NAtagadA sat/I /
     va/S/AM ca vidy/An nArada brAhmaN/As t/arhy eSy\AH //16//
|p17  y/a enAm /ava/SAm /Aha dev/AnAM n/ihitaM nidh/im /
     ubha/u t/asmai bhavA/Sarva/u parikr/amy/eSum asyatah //17//
|p18  y/o asyA /Udho n/a ved/Atho asyA st/anAn ut/a /
     ubh/ayenaiv/Asmai duhe d/AtuM c/ed /a/Sakad va/S/Am //18//
|p19  duradabhna/inam /A /Saye yAcit/AM ca n/a d/itsati /
     n/Asmai k/AmAH s/am .rdhyante y/Am /adattvA c/ikIrSati //19//
|p20  dev/A va/S/Am ayAcan m/ukhaM k.rtv/A br/AhmaNam /
     t/eSAM s/arveSAm /adadad dh/eDaM ny \eti m/AnuSaH //20//
|p21  h/eDaM pa/SUn/AM ny \eti brAhmaN/ebhy/o 'dadad va/S/Am /
     dev/AnAM n/ihitaM bhAg/aM m/artya/S c/en nipriyAy/ate //21//
|p22  y/ad any/e /Sat/aM y/Aceyur brAhmaN/A g/opatiM va/S/Am /
     /athainAM dev/A abruvann ev/aM ha vid/uSo va/S/A //22//
|p23  y/a ev/aM vid/uSe 'dattv/AthAny/ebhyo d/adad va/S/Am /
     durg/A t/asmA adhiSTh/Ane p.rthiv/I sah/adevatA //23//
