|p39  /Asyai brAhmaN/AH sn/apanIr harantv /avIraghnIr /ud ajantv /ApaH /
     aryamN/o agn/iM p/ary etu pUSan pr/atIkSante /Sv/a/Suro dev/ara/S ca //39//
