|c3
|p1  iy/aM n/ArI patilok/aM v.rNAn/A n/i padyata /upa tvA martya pr/etam /
     dh/armaM purAN/am anupAl/ayantI t/asyai praj/AM dr/aviNaM ceh/a dhehi //1//
