     hastagrAbh/asya dadhiS/os t/aved/aM p/atyur janitv/am abh/i s/aM babhUtha //2//
|p3  /apa/SyaM yuvat/iM nIy/amAnAM jIv/AM m.rt/ebhyaH pariNIy/amAnAm /
     andh/ena y/at t/amasA pr/Av.rt/AsIt prAkt/o /apAcIm anayaM t/ad enAm //3//
|p4  prajAnaty \aghnye jIvalok/aM dev/AnAM p/anthAm anusaMc/arantI /
     ay/aM te g/opatis t/aM juSasva svarg/aM lok/am /adhi rohayainam //4//
