     ky/AmbUr /atra rohatu /SANDadUrv/A vy\alka/SA //6//
|p7  id/aM ta /ekam pur/a U ta /ekaM t.rt/Iyena jy/otiSA s/aM vi/Sasva /
     saMv/e/Sane tanv\A3 c/Arur edhi priy/o dev/AnAM param/e sadh/asthe //7//
