     t/atra tv/aM pit/rbhiH saMvidAn/aH s/aM s/omena m/adasva s/aM svadh/AbhiH //8//
|p9  pr/a cyavasva tanv\a1M s/aM bharasva m/A te g/AtrA v/i hAyi m/o /S/arIram /
     m/ano n/iviSTam anus/aMvi/Sasva y/atra bh/Umer juS/ase t/atra gaccha //9//
