|p54  /atharvA pUrN/am camas/am y/am indrAy/Abibhar vAj/inIvate /
     t/asmin k.rNoti suk.rt/asya bhakS/aM t/asmin /induH pavate vi/Svad/An/im //54//
|p55  y/at te k.rSN/aH /Sakun/a Atut/oda pipIl/aH sarp/a ut/a vA /Sv/ApadaH /
     agn/iS T/ad vi/Sv/Ad agad/aM k.rNotu s/oma/S ca y/o brAhmaN/A~M Aviv/e/Sa //55//
|p56  p/ayasvatIr /oSadhayaH p/ayasvan mAmak/aM p/ayaH /
     ap/AM p/ayaso y/at p/ayas t/ena mA sah/a /Sumbhatu //56//
|p57  im/A n/ArIr avidhav/AH sup/atnIr /A~Njanena sarp/iSA s/aM sp.r/SantAm /
     ana/Sr/avo anamIv/AH sur/atnA /A rohantu j/anayo y/onim /agre //57//
|p58  s/aM gacchasva pit/rbhiH s/aM yam/eneSTApUrt/ena param/e vy\oman /
     hitv/Avady/aM p/unar /astam /ehi s/aM gacchatAM tanv\A suv/arcAH //58//
|p59  y/e naH pit/uH pit/aro y/e pitAmah/A y/a Avivi/S/ur urv \a1nt/arikSam /
     t/ebhyaH svar/Ad /asunItir no ady/a vathAva/S/aM tanv\aH kalpayAti //59//
