     yaj~N/am im/aM c/atasraH prad/i/So vardhayantu saMsrAvy\eNa hav/iSA juhomi //3//
|c2
|p1  /S/aM ta /Apo haimavat/IH /S/am u te santUtsy\AH /
     /S/aM te saniSyad/A /ApaH /S/am u te santu varSy\AH //1//
|p2  /S/aM ta /Apo dhanvany\A3H /S/aM te santv anUpy\AH /
     /S/aM te khanitr/imA /ApaH /S/aM y/AH kumbh/ebhir /Abh.rtAH //2//
